s:2647:"<p>The Comfort for you module on the demo home page is an example of using the Zenshortcode plugin to render a grid of content as well as font icons.</p>
<p><img src="/docs/medica/images/frontpage/comfort-for-you.jpg" alt="Comfort for you" /></p>
<h4>Steps to recreate this module</h4>
<p>This module is a custom html module published to the grid8 module position.</p>
<ol>
<li>Navigate to the module manager in your Joomla administrator via extensions &gt; Module Manager</li>
<li>Click new</li>
<li>Select the custom html type module</li>
<li>Copy the markup displayed below into the text area of the custom module.</li>
<li>Assign the module to a module position (grid8).</li>
<li>Ensure the moduel is published</li>
<li>Give the module a title</li>
<li>Set the module title to be hidden</li>
<li>Save your new module.</li>
</ol>
